.TH WLA\-65CE02 1 "November 2023" "WLA-DX 10.6" "WLA DX Assembler"
.SH NAME
wla\-65ce02 \- WLA DX cross-assembler for the CSG 65CE02
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wla\-65ce02
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.B \-o
.I output.o
.I source.asm
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wla\-65ce02
assembles CSG 65CE02 source code to a WLA DX object file.
The 65CE02 is an enhanced 6502 variant used in the Commodore 65 and Amiga CD32 joypad controller.
.PP
All WLA DX assemblers share an identical command-line interface.
For full option descriptions, examples, and a list of all supported CPU
architectures, see
.BR wla\-6502 (1).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wla\-6502 (1),
.BR wlalink (1)
